      "description": "The FEA modeling framework predicts construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement within pre-established acceptance bounds (relative error <10% and E/uval <1.96) for the non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw under ASTM F1717 static compression-bending loading. This claim is central to the regulatory submission supporting 510(k) clearance and is considered validated across the two independent laboratory datasets.",
